    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "\ud83d\udd27 **Budget-Friendly Project Car \u2014 Perfect for the DIY Enthusiast!** Looking for an affordable opportunity to get behind the wheel or tackle a fun project? This one's for you! This car is in poor condition \u2014 it has visible wear, some mechanical issues, and will need attention before it's road-ready. That said, it's priced to reflect exactly what it is, making it a fantastic starting point for a handy buyer or someone in need of parts. If you love a challenge and want to stretch your dollar, don't let this one pass you by! \ud83d\udee0\ufe0f",
      "price": 6000.0,
