      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Honest Value for the Budget-Conscious Buyer \u2014 A No-Frills Runner at a Real Deal Price! This used car is in poor condition, and we're keeping it real with you \u2014 it shows its age and has accumulated its share of wear and tear over the years. That said, it represents a genuine opportunity for a handy buyer, a first-time driver on a tight budget, or someone looking for a project vehicle. The price reflects the condition honestly, so what you see is what you get \u2014 no surprises! If you're looking for affordable wheels and don't mind putting in a little TLC, this could be your next ride.",
      "price": 6000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed honestly to reflect its true current condition \u2014 it is in poor shape and is best suited for a buyer who understands they are purchasing a project car or a basic transportation option requiring attention. The car has visible wear and damage, including body imperfections, interior deterioration, and mechanical issues that will need to be addressed. It is drivable but not without its problems, and prospective buyers should plan for repair costs after purchase. We recommend a thorough inspection prior to buying. That said, at this price point, it offers an accessible entry for mechanically inclined buyers or those on a tight budget who are willing to invest some work into getting it roadworthy and presentable.",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in good, solid condition \u2014 a dependable used car that has been conscientiously maintained and is ready for its next owner without requiring immediate repairs. The exterior presents well, showing only minor, age-appropriate blemishes such as light surface scratches and small door dings consistent with normal daily use \u2014 nothing that detracts significantly from its overall appearance. The paint retains good depth and shine, and the body panels are straight and free of rust or significant damage. Inside, the cabin is clean and functional; the upholstery shows moderate wear on the driver's seat and high-touch areas, but there are no tears, stains, or broken components. All major systems \u2014 engine, transmission, brakes, and HVAC \u2014 are in proper working order, and the car drives smoothly and confidently. Tires have reasonable tread remaining, and all lights and electronics function as expected. This is an honest, everyday driver that offers solid value for a buyer looking for reliability without paying a premium for showroom-level condition.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed at $48,000, a price that genuinely reflects its outstanding mint condition \u2014 and we stand behind that assessment completely. The exterior is virtually flawless: the paint shines with a deep, rich luster that rivals a showroom finish, with no visible scratches, chips, dents, or swirl marks. Body panel gaps are tight and uniform, and all trim pieces, moldings, and chrome accents are pristine and properly fitted. The interior is equally impressive \u2014 the seats, carpets, headliner, and dashboard all appear as though they've barely been touched, with no fading, cracking, staining, or wear to speak of. All electronics, climate controls, infotainment systems, and power features function exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine bay is clean and well-maintained, with no leaks, corrosion, or signs of neglect. The vehicle runs smoothly and quietly, with responsive handling and braking that inspire full confidence. Service records indicate consistent, proper maintenance throughout its life. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle that has been exceptionally well cared for \u2014 a true turn-key purchase for a discerning buyer who expects nothing but the best.",
      "price": 48000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
